{"type": "article", "id": 16684, "title": "斜纹木柜", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-28T06:14:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122437aDSCORFglN7jbWLT.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这些带斜纹的柜子来自意大利设计团队 Baroli Design ，他们由 6 位设计师组成。深浅相间的纹路源于英国传统的人字纹，用桉树和橡树的自然颜色混合镶嵌，有一种奇异的几何美感。柜子下的铁制支架也有相应的转折，与柜子一样多了一份趣味，也让它显得轻盈。<a href=\"http://www.bartolidesign.it/BartoliDesign/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">这里是他们的主页。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614395440YpZ72clI9jAbGB.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"899\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143954rAUmGyizgsO0D9M4.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"383\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143955bRVoF2Cf654DcZML.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143955ZlEv4L8Wza7MQo0T.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"747\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.245\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}